Package: vcglR
Title: Victorian gambling data in tidy format
Version: 0.1.6
Authors@R: 
    person("Sam", "Gow", , "sam.gow@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains Victorian gambling data in tidy formats. Current data is limited
    to annual gaming machine data by venue and monthly gaming machine data by local government area.
    Refer to README for details of latest data.
